<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document Expired - Action Required - Carbon Cube Kenya</title>
  </head>

  <body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background-color: #f9fafb; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <div style="max-width: 620px; margin: 30px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
      <div style="background: #1f2937; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 25px 20px;">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 100%;">
          <div style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle;">
            <img src="https://carboncube-ke.com/logo.png" alt="Carbon Cube Kenya" style="height: 50px; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px;" />
            <span style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-align: middle;">ARBONCUBE</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af;">Kenya's Most Trusted Online Marketplace</p>
      </div>
      
      <div style="padding: 30px 25px;">
        <h1 style="color: #111827; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 24px;">Document Expired - Action Required</h1>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: left;">Hello <strong><%= @seller.fullname %></strong>,</p>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">Your document (<span style="color: #fbbf24; font-weight: 600;"><%= @seller.document_type.name %></span>) expired on <span style="color: #fbbf24; font-weight: 600;"><%= @seller.document_expiry_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %></span>.</p>

        <div style="background: #fef3c7; border: 1px solid #fbbf24; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; color: #92400e; font-size: 14px;">
          <p style="margin: 0;">
            <strong>Urgent Action Required:</strong> Please update your document immediately to keep your account verified and active.
          </p>
          <p style="margin-top: 10px;"><strong>Document Type:</strong> <%= @seller.document_type.name %></p>
          <p><strong>Expired On:</strong> <%= @seller.document_expiry_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %></p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
          <a href="<%= @update_url %>" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #fbbf24; color: #111827; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px;">Update Document Now</a>
        </div>

        <div style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 18px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 15px; color: #374151;">
          <h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #111827; text-align: left;">Account Status Impact</h3>
          <p>• <strong>Verification Required</strong> - Your account verification is pending document update</p>
          <p>• <strong>Service Continuity</strong> - Update now to avoid any service interruptions</p>
          <p>• <strong>Compliance</strong> - Meet regulatory requirements for continued operation</p>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 30px;">Best regards,<br>
        <strong>The Carbon Cube Kenya Team</strong></p>

        <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 30px 0;">
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280;">
          This is an automated reminder. Please update your document to maintain account verification.
          For assistance, contact us at +254 712 990 524.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
          <img src="https://carboncube-ke.com/logo.png" alt="Carbon Cube Kenya" style="height: 25px; width: 25px; opacity: 0.7;" />
        </div>
        <p><strong>Carbon Cube Kenya</strong> | 9th Floor, CMS Africa, Nairobi</p>
        <p>Phone: +254 712 990 524 | Email: <%= ENV['BREVO_EMAIL'] %></p>
        <p>© 2025 Carbon Cube Kenya. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>